Class DefaultProductIon

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<ProductIon>, PeptideIon, ProductIon

    public class DefaultProductIon
extends AbstractProductIon
    Default implement of AbstractProductIon. In tandem mass spectrum, the level 1 mass generate precursor ions. For a special precursor ion, based on product ion type, cleavage position, product ion charge to generate a product ion.
    Author:
    Qingwei XU

    • Constructor Detail

      • DefaultProductIon

        public DefaultProductIon(PrecursorIon precursorIon,
                 ProductIonType type,
                 int position,
                 Peptide peptide,
                 int charge)
        Create product ion instance. There are some constraints among the PrecursorIon, ProductIonType, cleavage position, and the ProductIon.

        Notice: Not suggest user to create a instance by calling construct method directly.

        Reference AbstractPrecursorIon.getProductIon(uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.mol.ProductIonType, int, int) see how to generate the product ion.
        Parameters:
        precursorIon - should not set null! Otherwise throw NullPointerException.
        type - should not set null! Otherwise throw NullPointerException.
        position - from [1..precursor.peptide.length-1]
        peptide - product ion peptide. should not set null! Otherwise throw NullPointerException.
        charge - from [1..3], should not great than precursor ion charges.
